data.description: ASSUMABLE LOAN 2.75%! NEW renovated bathroom, NEW kitchen appliances, NEW Light/Fan fixtures, EXTENDED back porch with a Cowboy Pool, and MORE! Ask for the seller upgrade list! The Roof, HVAC & hot water heater is 6 years old! This charming, 3-bedroom home offers a ton of natural light, an open floor plan, and a huge backyard space, perfect for entertaining! Walk up to a beautiful front porch with a ton of space for chairs and relaxation. As you step inside, you’ll discover an entirely modern home, situated within a stone's throw of premium retail and dining options such as Target, Cinemark Movie Theater, Home Depot, and more. Only 25 minutes to Downtown Austin with easy access to highways 45 and 130. Do you love the outdoors? You’re within walking distance of Wilbarger Creek Park, Highland Park's community pool, and the dog park. Your future home features expansive bedrooms, an oversized garage space, and stylish tile flooring in the living areas. Storage is plentiful, ensuring a clutter-free lifestyle. The backyard has an extended 10X10 porch with a unique "Cowboy Pool," ideal for entertaining or simply enjoying the Texas sun. This property also features a fresh exterior paint job, new carpeting, sophisticated kitchen hardware, updated doorknobs, a Nest thermostat, and more! This home is ready to welcome you—just ask your realtor for the assumable loan qualification details. Welcome home!
